name: 5-methyltetrahydropteroyltriglutamate---homocysteine S-methyltransferase
comment: Requires phosphate and contains zinc. The enzyme from Escherichia coli also requires a reducing system. Unlike EC 2.1.1.13, methionine synthase, this enzyme does not contain cobalamin.
